@startuml
!theme cerulean
title UC-05 - Activity Diagram: Perform Data Transformation & Mapping

start

:1. Receive raw record from Ingestion Layer;

:2. Load compiled Field Rules from Meta-Schema Cache 
   (Target-Driven);

:3. Initialize target record (optimized size);

repeat
  :4. For each Target Field Rule;
  :5. Get source value;
  if (Value exists?) then (Yes)
    :6. Trim whitespace;
    :7. Apply XREF (if configured);
    :8. Perform Type Casting;
  else (No)
    :9. Apply Default Value;
  endif

  :10. Validate required field;
  if (Validation Failed?) then (Yes)
    :Push record to DLQ;
    detach
  endif
repeat while (More fields?)

:11. Return clean transformed record;

stop

@enduml